Episodes.Title: Episode #1.1
Episodes.Plot: A new edgy Australian sketch comedy series starring six new Australian teen actors who perform sketches about zombies, cavemen, naughty girl guides as well as parodies of twilight and talent shows.

Episodes.Title: Episode #1.2
Episodes.Plot: Introducing Mario and his faithful assistant Luigi outside their computer game world. Watch as Voldemort tries to win a board game and the kids of Jolimont High Witness News follow the case of the missing pencil case.

Episodes.Title: Episode #1.3
Episodes.Plot: This episode continues the arguments of Mario and Luigi as they get their hands dirty, see the latest audition from Australia's next big talent and listen to the cavemen as they talk about maths.

Episodes.Title: Episode #1.4
Episodes.Plot: This episode sees Mario and Luigi contemplate going back to their old gaming career, while Bella tries to get through to Edward in the latest Twilight Oz Style.

Episodes.Title: Episode #1.5
Episodes.Plot: At Viking High it's time for the all important sex-ed class. The cast are put through a rigorous spelling bee, and the new fad, Puddlejumping, continues its march to world domination.
